OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777050359
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of
OL,4,Ccannabis seized in crackdown
OL,6,FImitation firearms, a taser, cash and
OL,7,Fcannabis worth #588,000 has been
OL,8,Fseized as police target organised
OL,9,Fcriminal gangs in Hampshire.
OL,11,FA month-long operation saw Hampshire
OL,12,FPolice conduct dawn raids across the
OL,13,Fcounty, unearthing six illegal
OL,14,Fcannabis grow sites in Farnborough,
OL,15,FAldershot, and Southampton.
OL,17,FThousands of cannabis plants and
OL,18,Fprocessed cannabis ready for street
OL,19,Fsupply was seized, as well as an
OL,20,Fimitation firearm, over #10,000 of
OL,21,Fcash and 10 mobile phones.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
