PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777050359
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of
OL,4,Ccannabis seized in crackdown
OL,6,FCar wash sites were also visited as
OL,7,Fpart of the operation to crackdown on
OL,8,Fillegal immigration, modern slavery,
OL,9,Fand human trafficking offences.
OL,11,FSpecialist officers carried out a
OL,12,Fvaluation of just one harvest,
OL,13,Festimating the illegal grows to be
OL,14,Fworth more than #234,000.
OL,16,FActivity took place throughout the
OL,17,Fmonth of March and early April as the
OL,18,Fforce participated in Operation Mille,
OL,19,Fa national operation targeting
OL,20,Fcriminal networks involved in cannabis
OL,21,Fcultivation and money laundering.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
