OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777050359
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of
OL,4,Ccannabis seized in crackdown
OL,6,FThe early morning raids were executed
OL,7,Ffollowing intelligence reports from
OL,8,Fthe local community, with one property
OL,9,Fbeing identified after engineers
OL,10,Fattended the location to carry out
OL,11,Froutine work and noted a strong smell
OL,12,Fof cannabis.
OL,14,FTen people in total were arrested as
OL,15,Fpart of the operation, eight have now
OL,16,Fbeen charged, while two men were
OL,17,Fsafeguarded as suspected victims of
OL,18,Fhuman trafficking.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
