OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777050359
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of
OL,4,Ccannabis seized in crackdown
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Christian Reid
OL,7,FMilligan who led the coordinated
OL,8,Foperation said: "These latest
OL,9,Fsuccesses are a result of intricate
OL,10,Fand painstaking work by numerous teams
OL,11,Facross the force, and I would like to
OL,12,Fthank them for their efforts which
OL,13,Fhave paid off immensely.
OL,15,F"Executing warrants linked to cannabis
OL,16,Fcultivation is something our officers
OL,17,Fcarry out regularly as part of our
OL,18,Fwork to protect communities and target
OL,19,Forganised crime. By targeting cannabis
OL,20,Fcultivation, we're cutting the issue
OL,21,Foff at the source.
OL,26,@pD@QOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777050359
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of
OL,4,Ccannabis seized in crackdown
OL,6,F"Without activity like this, these
OL,7,Fplants would be harvested, processed
OL,8,Fand disseminated in our community
OL,9,Ffuelling criminality, anti-social
OL,10,Fbehaviour and the appalling violence
OL,11,Fwe see when drug gangs feud over
OL,12,Fterritory.
OL,14,F"Cannabis farms are not victimless.
OL,15,FThey are often linked to other
OL,16,Fcriminality, including serious
OL,17,Fviolence, anti-social behaviour and
OL,18,Fthe exploitation of vulnerable people,
OL,19,Fwho are frequently forced to live and
OL,20,Fwork in unsafe and inhumane conditions.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
