PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777050359
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of
OL,4,Ccannabis seized in crackdown
OL,6,F"These properties are also at
OL,7,Fsignificant risk of fire due to
OL,8,Fillegal electricity bypasses and other
OL,9,Fdangerous modifications. That risk can
OL,10,Fextend to neighbouring homes, putting
OL,11,Finnocent members of the public in
OL,12,Fserious danger.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
