OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777050359
OL,3,CHalf a million pounds worth of
OL,4,Ccannabis seized in crackdown
OL,6,F"In addition to the work of our
OL,7,Fofficers, it's the information
OL,8,Freceived from members of the public
OL,9,Fthat informs our activity. I would
OL,10,Flike to encourage the community to
OL,11,Fcontinue to tell us what you know and
OL,12,Fraise the alarm when things don't seem
OL,13,Fright. With your support we're ridding
OL,14,Four community of illegal drugs and
OL,15,Fapprehending those fuelling it."
OL,17,FSigns to look out for include:
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
